The paper deals with building a CNN-based ear recognition model, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses data augmentation techniques, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM) research. The paper addresses the issue of limited training data, which is a concern in cryptography and security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
